#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:444
msgid "1.2.4 (2024-05-05)"
msgstr "1.2.4 (2024-05-05)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:446
msgid "**内置策略**   修复 MACDEXT、WILLR、AROONOSC、SLPHT 等策略 bug。"
