#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:463
msgid "1.2.1 (2024-04-25)"
msgstr "1.2.1 (2024-04-25)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:465
msgid "**打包**   修正 1.2.0 样式文件未打入包的问题。"
msgstr ""
"**Packaging** Fixed the issue where style files were not included in the "
"package in version 1.2.0."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:467
msgid "**live 账户 API**   新增 `live_trade_accounts()` 返回各账户详情。"
msgstr ""
"The **Live Accounts API** now includes `live_trade_accounts()`, which returns "
"details for each account."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:469
msgid "**CLI**   修正 trade info 格式；live 相关配置帮助改进。"
msgstr ""
"**CLI** Corrected the trade info format; improved live-related configurations."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:472
msgid "1.2.0 (2024-04-25)"
msgstr "Version 1.2.0 (2024-04-25)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:474
msgid ""
"**Trader TUI**   新增终端 UI，与 Trader Shell 二选一（`live_trade_ui_type`）；内"
"置亮/暗主题；展示账户、持仓、订单与日志；Ctrl+P / Ctrl+R 暂停恢复。"
msgstr ""
"**Trader TUI** adds a new terminal UI, offering a choice between Trader Shell "
"(`live_trade_ui_type`); includes built-in light/dark themes; displays accounts, "
"positions, orders, and logs; and allows Ctrl+P / Ctrl+R to pause and resume."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:477
msgid "1.1.11 (2024-04-20)"
msgstr "1.1.11 (2024-04-20)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:479
msgid "**refill_data_source**   支持可调批次大小与间隔的分批下载。"
msgstr ""
"**refill_data_source** supports batch downloads with adjustable batch size and "
"interval."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:481
msgid "**配置错误提示**   配置键非法值时错误信息更友好。"
msgstr ""
"**Configuration Error Prompts** The error messages are now more user-friendly "
"when configuring keys with invalid values."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:484
msgid "1.1.10 (2024-04-19)"
msgstr "1.1.10 (2024-04-19)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:486
msgid "**tushare 重试**   修复 tushare 自动重试相关配置不生效的问题。"
msgstr ""
"**tushare Retry** Fixed an issue where tushare automatic retry configurations "
"were not working."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:489
msgid "1.1.9 (2024-04-09)"
msgstr "Version 1.1.9 (2024-04-09)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:491
msgid "**分钟数据**   修复本地分钟数据提取偶发错误；兼容性改进。"
msgstr ""
"**Minute Data** Fixed occasional errors in local minute data extraction; "
"improved compatibility."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:494
msgid "1.1.8 (2024-04-05)"
msgstr "1.1.8 (2024-04-05)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:496
msgid ""
"**Python 3.9–3.12**   扩展支持；兼容 pandas 2.2.1、numpy 1.26.4、numba 0.59.1；"
"修复 3.10+ 策略优化失败；若干错误信息改进。"
msgstr ""
"**Python 3.9–3.12** Extended support; compatible with pandas 2.2.1, numpy "
"1.26.4, and numba 0.59.1; fixed strategy optimization failures in 3.10+; "
"improved several error messages."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:499
msgid "1.1.7 (2024-04-03)"
msgstr "1.1.7 (2024-04-03)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:501
msgid "**Python 版本**   官方支持 Python 3.9～3.12 安装运行。"
msgstr ""
"**Python Version** Officially supports Python 3.9 to 3.12 for installation and "
"operation."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:504
msgid "1.1.4 (2024-03-30)"
msgstr "1.1.4 (2024-03-30)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:506
msgid ""
"**依赖冲突**   调整 numba/numpy 版本约束；首次加载警告略改进；修复 pandas > 2.0 "
"兼容问题；优化算法 2 在部分 numpy/numba 组合下的性能警告。"
msgstr ""
"**Dependency Conflicts** Adjusted numba/numpy version constraints; slightly "
"improved initial load warnings; fixed pandas > 2.0 compatibility issues; "
"optimized performance warnings for Algorithm 2 under certain numpy/numba "
"combinations."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:509
msgid "1.1.3 (2024-03-25)"
msgstr "1.1.3 (2024-03-25)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:511
msgid ""
"**回测结果**   回测返回 dict 新增 `trade_log`、`trade_records`、"
"`full_histories` 键，便于直接访问。"
msgstr ""
"**Backtest Results** The backtest returned a dictionary with the added keys "
"`trade_log`, `trade_records`, and `full_histories` for easy access."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:514
msgid "1.1.2 (2024-03-18)"
msgstr "1.1.2 (2024-03-18)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:516
msgid "**CLI dashboard**   `dashboard --rewind` 可查看历史保存日志。"
msgstr "The CLI dashboard `dashboard --rewind` allows you to view saved logs."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:518
msgid "**CLI buy/sell**   提交结果打印更明确。"
msgstr "The CLI buy/sell submission results are printed more clearly."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:521
msgid "1.1.1 (2024-03-16)"
msgstr "1.1.1 (2024-03-16)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:523
msgid ""
"**live 系统日志**   不同 live 实例写入不同系统日志文件；支持从 live / 系统日志文"
"件读信息。"
msgstr ""
"**Live System Logs** Different live instances write to different system log "
"files; it also supports reading information from live/system log files."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:526
msgid "1.1.0 (2024-03-08)"
msgstr "Version 1.1.0 (2024-03-08)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:528
msgid ""
"**Trader Shell 参数解析**   全命令支持 `--parameter` / `-p` 风格及 `-h`/`--"
"help`；错误提示与用法说明改进。`watch` 支持 `-r` 移除、`-c` 清空；`buy`/`sell` "
"用 `-p` 价格、`-s` 方向；`info`/`overview` 增加 `--system`；`orders` 增加 "
"status/time/side/type 过滤；`config` 支持 `-s` 设置与 `-l` 层级；`strategies` 支"
"持 `--set-par`；`run` 支持 `--args` 传任务参数。"
msgstr ""
"**Trader Shell Parameter Parsing** Full command support for `--parameter` / `-"
"p` style and `-h` / `--help`; improved error messages and usage instructions. "
"`watch` now supports `-r` to remove and `-c` to clear; `buy` / `sell` uses `-p` "
"for price and `-s` for direction; `info` / `overview` adds `--system`; `orders` "
"adds status/time/side/type filtering; `config` supports `-s` for setting and `-"
"l` for hierarchy; `strategies` supports `--set-par`; `run` supports `--args` "
"for passing task parameters."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:531
msgid "1.0.27 (2024-03-05)"
msgstr "1.0.27 (2024-03-05)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:533
msgid ""
"**数据库读取**   移除通过 pandas SQL 读库路径，避免高版本 pandas 要求 "
"sqlalchemy 的 UserWarning。"
msgstr ""
"**Database Reads** Remove the pandas SQL read path to avoid the UserWarning "
"from SQLAlchemy required by higher versions of pandas."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:536
msgid "1.0.26 (2024-02-29)"
msgstr "1.0.26 (2024-02-29)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:538
msgid "**live 日志**   live 交易日志写入系统日志文件，以账户号为前缀区分。"
msgstr ""
"**Live Logs** Live transaction logs are written to the system log file and are "
"distinguished by the account number."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:541
msgid "1.0.25 (2024-02-28)"
msgstr "1.0.25 (2024-02-28)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:543
msgid ""
"**live trade_log 文件**   live 模式保存 trade log 文件至 `trade_log_file_path`；"
"若干 live bug 修复与错误信息打印。"
msgstr ""
"**Live trade_log file** Saves the trade log file to `trade_log_file_path` in "
"live mode; includes several live bug fixes and error message printing."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:546
msgid "1.0.24 (2024-02-18)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.24 (February 18, 2024)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:548
msgid ""
"**broker 回归**   修复 1.0.18 以来 broker 合并不完整导致 live 下单失败的问题。"
msgstr ""
"**Broker Returns** Fixed an issue since version 1.0.18 where incomplete broker "
"merging caused live order failures."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:551
msgid "1.0.23 (2024-02-15)"
msgstr "1.0.23 (2024-02-15)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:553
msgid "**filter_stocks / candle**   修复类型转换错误导致筛选与 K 线失败的问题。"
msgstr ""
"**filter_stocks / candle** Fixed an issue where a type conversion error caused "
"filtering and candlestick charts to fail."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:556
msgid "1.0.22 (2024-02-14)"
msgstr "1.0.22 (2024-02-14)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:558
msgid ""
"**get_config / candle**   修正 list 日期解析错误；进度条文本截断至屏宽；"
"`get_stock_info()` 无需全部基础表即可运行。"
msgstr ""
"**get_config / candle** Fixed a date parsing error in the list; truncated "
"progress bar text to screen width; `get_stock_info()` can now run without all "
"underlying tables."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:561
msgid "1.0.21 (2024-02-11)"
msgstr "1.0.21 (2024-02-11)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:563
msgid "**稳定性**   若干 bug 修复。"
msgstr "**Stability** Several bugs have been fixed."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:566
msgid "1.0.20 (2024-02-08)"
msgstr "1.0.20 (2024-02-08)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:568
msgid ""
"**免 TA-Lib 指标**   修正 EMA、MACD、TRIX、DEMA 在无 ta-lib 时的实现，结果与 "
"talib 版略有差异但可用。"
msgstr ""
"**TA-Lib-Free Indicators** Corrected the implementation of EMA, MACD, TRIX, and "
"DEMA without ta-lib. The results are slightly different from the ta-lib "
"version, but still usable."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:571
msgid "1.0.19 (2024-02-07)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.19 (2024-02-07)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:573
msgid ""
"**免 TA-Lib**   RSI、MA、BBANDS 不再依赖 ta-lib，无 ta-lib 也可画 K 线；降低初学"
"者依赖门槛。"
msgstr ""
"**TA-Lib-Free** RSI, MA, and BBANDS no longer depend on ta-lib, and candlestick "
"charts can be drawn without ta-lib; lowering the dependency threshold for "
"beginners."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:576
msgid "1.0.18 (2024-02-05)"
msgstr "1.0.18 (2024-02-05)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:578
msgid ""
"**Trader Shell 消息**   订单成交展示含股数与现金变化；INFO/OVERVIEW 默认不再打印"
"系统信息；numpy 版本要求更新。"
msgstr ""
"**Trader Shell Messages** Order completion display includes changes in share "
"quantity and cash; INFO/OVERVIEW no longer prints system information by "
"default; NumPy version update required."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:581
msgid "1.0.17 (2024-01-29)"
msgstr "1.0.17 (2024-01-29)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:583
msgid "**CLI run**   可在主线程运行策略便于调试。"
msgstr ""
"**CLI run** allows you to run strategies on the main thread for easier "
"debugging."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:585
msgid "**live 行情**   修复运行频率低于 1 小时时 live 价获取失败。"
msgstr ""
"**Live Price Quotes** Fixed an issue where live price retrieval failed when the "
"frequency of operation was less than 1 hour."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:588
msgid "1.0.16 (2024-01-27)"
msgstr "1.0.16 (2024-01-27)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:590
msgid "**信号无法下单提示**   live 模式现金/持仓不足无法转订单时会提示。"
msgstr ""
"**Order Placement Failure Not Notice** This message will appear when you are "
"unable to place an order in Live Mode due to insufficient cash/position."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:592
msgid ""
"**成交与成本**   修复重复处理成交导致可用量/现金错误、成本计算错误、history 命令"
"多标的成本错误；修复非交易日意外填数据（#85）等问题。"
msgstr ""
"**Transactions and Costs** Fixed issues such as errors in available quantity/"
"cash due to duplicate transaction processing, cost calculation errors, and cost "
"errors for multiple targets in the history command; fixed issues such as "
"unexpected data entry on non-trading days (#85)."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:595
msgid "1.0.15 (2023-12-29)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.15 (2023-12-29)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:597
msgid ""
"**指数与 ETF live**   支持监控指数/ETF live 价；live 交易目标支持 ETF 与指数。"
msgstr ""
"**Index & ETF Live** Supports monitoring index/ETF live prices; live trading "
"targets support both ETFs and indices."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:600
msgid "1.0.14 (2023-12-22)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.14 (2023-12-22)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:602
msgid "**依赖**   移除可选 sqlalchemy；broker 增加最大重试后停止执行。"
msgstr ""
"**Dependencies** Remove optional SQLAlchemy; increase maximum retries before "
"stopping execution on the broker."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:605
msgid "1.0.13 (2023-12-21)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.13 (2023-12-21)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:607
msgid ""
"**Trader Shell**   命令模式上下键翻阅历史；新增 `buy`/`sell` 手动下单；live 价后"
"台线程获取。"
msgstr ""
"**Trader Shell** Command Mode: Use the up and down arrow keys to navigate "
"through history; Add `buy`/`sell` manual order placement; Live price is "
"retrieved via a background thread."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:609
msgid "**Simulator Broker**   按 live 价返回模拟成交；修复订单互相阻塞。"
msgstr ""
"**Simulator Broker** Returns simulated trades at the live price; fixes order "
"blocking issues."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:612
msgid "1.0.12 (2023-12-07)"
msgstr "1.0.12 (2023-12-07)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:614
msgid ""
"**视觉与 live 价**   界面效果改进；live 价后台线程避免主循环卡顿；非本地时区也可"
"显示 live 价；监控刷新间隔可配置。"
msgstr ""
"**Visual and Live Price** UI improvements; Live price background thread "
"prevents main loop lag; Live price can be displayed even in non-local time "
"zones; Monitoring refresh interval is configurable."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:617
msgid "1.0.11 (2023-12-03)"
msgstr "1.0.11 (2023-12-03)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:619
msgid "**Shell 参数风格**   支持 `--parameter` / `-p` 新风格（旧风格将弃用）。"
msgstr ""
"**Shell parameter styles** Support the new styles `--parameter` / `-p` (the old "
"styles will be deprecated)."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:621
msgid ""
"**live 配置**   可配置 broker 参数与时区；ta-lib 改为可选，部分内置策略无 ta-"
"lib 仍可用。"
msgstr ""
"**Live Configuration** allows configuring broker parameters and timezone; ta-"
"lib is now optional, but some built-in strategies are still available even "
"without ta-lib."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:624
msgid "1.0.10 (2023-11-25)"
msgstr "1.0.10 (2023-11-25)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:626
msgid "**reference 数据**   修正 1.0.9 遗留的 reference None 错误。"
msgstr ""
"**Reference Data** Fixed the \"reference None\" error that was a legacy issue "
"from version 1.0.9."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:628
msgid "**backtest_price_adj**   默认值改为 `none`。"
msgstr "The default value of **backtest_price_adj** should be changed to `none`."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:631
msgid "1.0.9 (2023-11-24)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.9 (2023-11-24)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:633
msgid "**reference 数据**   修正 reference 生成与注入策略的逻辑。"
msgstr ""
"**Reference Data** Corrected the logic of reference generation and injection "
"strategy."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:635
msgid "**文档**   文档改进。"
msgstr "**Documentation** Documentation improvements."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:638
msgid "1.0.8 (2023-11-22)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.8 (2023-11-22)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:640
msgid ""
"**Trader Shell**   依赖 `rich` 的消息着色；文档发布至 Read the Docs；新增 "
"`qteasy.__version__`。"
msgstr ""
"**Trader Shell** now relies on `rich` for message coloring; documentation "
"published to Read the Docs; `qteasy.__version__` added."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:643
msgid "1.0.7 (2023-11-11)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.7 (2023-11-11)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:645
msgid "**Strategy**   新增 `use_latest_data_cycle` 控制是否用最新价生成信号。"
msgstr ""
"**Strategy** adds `use_latest_data_cycle` to control whether to use the latest "
"price to generate signals."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:647
msgid ""
"**Shell watch**   新增 `watch` 实时监控价；Shell 显示股票名称；东方财富 live 价"
"渠道。"
msgstr ""
"**Shell watch** Added `watch` for real-time price monitoring; Shell displays "
"stock names; Eastmoney Live price channel."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:650
msgid "1.0.6 (2023-10-19)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.6 (2023-10-19)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:652
msgid "**Shell config**   新增 `config` 命令。"
msgstr "**Shell config** Adds the `config` command."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:654
msgid "**FUND**   支持 FUND 作为投资类型。"
msgstr "**FUND** supports FUND as an investment type."

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:657
msgid "1.0.0 (2023-09-19)"
msgstr "Version 1.0.0 (2023-09-19)"

#: ../../source/RELEASE_HISTORY.md:659
msgid "**首次 PyPI 发布**   qteasy 首个可在 PyPI 安装使用的正式版本。"
msgstr ""
"**First PyPI Release** qteasy is the first official version that can be "
"installed and used on PyPI."
